        "text": "AIIP, the Italian Association of Internet Providers, welcomes the European Commission's initiative to address unfair digital practices and improve consumer protection. As a historic association representing over 60 SMEs operating in the digital sector across Italy, we support any initiative that protects citizens and strengthens a competitive and transparent market. However, it is essential that new rules avoid overburdening responsible and law-abiding small businesses, while ensuring strict oversight on the major players whose practices are at the core of today's digital imbalances.",
